        "- the values of the correlation are between -1 and 1.\n",
        "- negative values imply a negative linear association between the two variable.\n",
        "- positive values imply a positive linear association between the two variable.\n",
        "- corrolations closer to -1 or 1 suggest strong or associations and close to 0 imply no linear association.\n",
